message.body: I have an overfill of parking requests. You want a car for Friday ? I'll split proceeds with you
Yeah, we can fit a car. Sounds great! What's the rate?
I've got a friend parking on Friday and a coworker on Saturday. But we also have the two on-street parking passes.
Ok. Will u give them ur driveway then ? Probably $50
Yeah, sounds good. We can talk tonight to figure out logistics.
OK, you are confirmed for Kevin in your driveway for Friday.
